ulog (1.1.1-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Add session management with unique session IDs
  * Add USB device identity tracking (vendor:product:serial)
  * Add ulog-export tool for listing and exporting sessions
  * Add /etc/ulog.d/ multi-device config directory
  * Update documentation

